{"tid":1744351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大個心態愈仆街","createTime":"2019-11-21T16:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T16:24:05.000Z","uid":238801,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"411f4ad1fc5259123a5f33ad23cbf488f0d8498e","tid":1744351,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"成日覺得啲嘢煩就想嚟手劈埋一邊唔理<br />\n連人都係咁 一厭/覺得煩又唔理<br />\n好撚仆街真係抵我成日單機<br />\n但真係好易覺得人地好煩好麻煩唔想理佢<br />\n但又會好內疚尤其其實人地好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉 屌 真係好撚煩 其實真係覺得自己性格好乞人憎 但冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似食飯咁 有一排好鍾意某樣嘢就日日食<br />\n食咗嗰幾月就厭到一啖都唔想再食<br />\n到底我有咩問題<br />\n但個問題係 嘢食嘅話 即使我日後個口味死灰復燃都可以食番<br />\n但人同事唔同<br />\n錯過咗變咗唔係有得好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉好撚憎自己咁乞人憎 <br />\n屌<br />\n好撚煩"},{"pid":"2325ffe6ad33266ebbda529a788666a77a64f5ee","tid":1744351,"uid":130488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"Marco Rubio 官方Youtube 出左片仲唔同我入去多謝佢！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtube.com/watch?v=SkiJMOfGXXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSkiJMOfGXXc&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt81tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=9b954cbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">youtube.com/watch?v=SkiJMOfGXXc</a>"},{"pid":"ac1f2a07e6a8fa8f91d946eb476d009e6a565be7","tid":1744351,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"我中出完條女會一腳申佢左落床<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a154080de529ff27eba9c4c43f2cf743cb85c9","tid":1744351,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:14:55.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"7cb6b29969a7389af8a6b13968ace88f391726e0","tid":1744351,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚想再理其他人感受自己行先"},{"pid":"c419d869ebe2bda15726995